### 3.2 Semantic HTML Requirements
| Element | Requirement |
|---------|-------------|
| `<header>` | Site header ONLY |
| `<nav aria-label="...">` | Every navigation block |
| `<main id="main">` | Exactly ONE per page |
| `<section aria-labelledby="...">` | Thematic grouping with accessible label |
| `<article>` | Self-contained, syndication-ready content |
| `<aside>` | Tangential content |
| `<footer>` | Site footer ONLY |
| `<h1>`‚Äì`<h6>` | Strict hierarchy, NO skipped levels |
| `<button>` | Actions (not navigation) |
| `<a href="">` | Navigation (not actions) |
| `<figure>`/`<figcaption>` | Images with captions |

### 3.3 SEO Requirements (MANDATORY)
- **Title:** Unique, 50-60 chars, primary keyword first, brand last
- **Meta Description:** Unique, 150-160 chars, compelling CTA
- **Canonical:** Self-referencing on every page
- **JSON-LD:** `Organization`, `WebSite`, `WebPage` minimum
- **Open Graph / Twitter Cards:** Complete set
- **Sitemap:** `/sitemap.xml` at root
- **Robots:** `/public/robots.txt` allowing all, disallowing `/admin/`, `/api/`, `/private/`

