## 8. QA PIPELINE CONTRACT (MANDATORY ‚Äî from `@orchestrator` workflow)

### 8.1 Mandatory Gate Sequence
```
1. PLAN (Design Thinking)           ‚Üí @orchestrator + User approval
2. BUILD (frontend-dev)             ‚Üí @frontend-dev
3. CODE REVIEW (code-review)        ‚Üí @code-review ‚Üí STATUS: APPROVED
4. TEST PLAN (playwright-test-planner)  ‚Üí @playwright-test-planner
